  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/8403876/" class="title-link">国际政治角度--万事万物息息相关</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-8403876"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/63734696/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u63734696-2.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/63734696/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">安可</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar50 main-title-rating" title="力荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2017-03-08"
      class="main-meta">2017-03-08 00:12:18</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_8403876_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  太平天国对于中国的影响不可谓不大，再之后的数百年的中国革命中，都见到这个天国的影子。只不过它是先驱，先倒在了历史的洪流之中。 曾国藩之成功、太平天国之倒下，不是纯粹简单的因素就可以分析出来的。裴士锋站在国际政治的角度，查阅了许多英美历史资料，才让我们见到了历...

                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">1有用 / 0没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_8403876_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_8403876_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>





